snippet.title: Wow AH Has A Baby???
snippet.description:
If you could ever truly "knock me over with a feather "  this news definitely could cause it.  Amber Heard has welcomed her daughter into the world and just announced it.  

You can help me with the expenses of running this channel and attending the VA trial by donating to my PayPal at https://paypal.me/TammyTalksAbout?locale.x=en_US
